Interface Movable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.jsfml.graphics.Drawable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Bullet
    public interface Movable
extends org.jsfml.graphics.Drawable
    Any object that can be moved should implement this interface so that all objects on the screen can be moved as part of one single loop in the main class
